s=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off the dangers of Pandora as you embrace the precision of traditional Na’vi weapons, including your bow and spear-thrower, or leverage your human training with more destructive weapons, such as an assault rifle or a shotgun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHARE YOUR ADVENTURE IN FULL CAMPAIGN CO-OP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840770/extras/abfcc748278254a1a09be780c900f0d1.poster.avif?t=1769463197\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840770/extras/abfcc748278254a1a09be780c900f0d1.webm?t=1769463197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the full story campaign in single-player or with a friend online in two-player co-op.</p>",
